walkthrough.askAzure.description.message:
Enter @azure in the GitHub Copilot Chat to start a conversation.
 @azure can help with learning about Azure, deploying resources, troubleshooting web app problems, querying Azure costs and more without having to switch to the Azure Portal.
[Chat with @azure](command:azureResourceGroups.askAzure?%5B%22What%20kinds%20of%20things%20can%20you%20help%20me%20with?%22%5D)
